  "title": "chore: merge develop into next",
  "body": "This syncs the `next` branch with the latest changes on the develop branch. Doing this from time to time will help maintaining the two different codebases.\r\n\r\n- We made the code a bit more robust on `develop` and added some tests that we can leverage on `next`.\r\n- An annoying part was the upgrade to Prettier 18 that doesn't format the same on the two branches.\r\n- The e-commerce example works on CodeSandbox on the `develop` branch.\r\n- Etc.",
